o", "timestamp": 1617667200, "is_pinned": false}, {"id": "UgzjTF7S8pyOAZb-P-h4AaABAg", "parent": "root", "text": "Hallo Frinends Two wheeler insurance Krvaa naa ka leyaa Call maa 9336654062 Bajaj Company", "like_count": 0, "author_id": "UCmQms0830Rp__4ER9obl5CQ", "author": "@ujjawalmishra4898", "author_thumbnail": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/YHF8y7erxAm22uNS7spDkYxq-p3mvgbmikjnT00BAQsB_B0GXMAYYpDLFOmP_BGgYedEdCwt5Q=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "author_is_uploader": false, "author_is_verified": false, "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/@ujjawalmishra4898", "is_favorited": false, "_time_text": "5 years ago", "timestamp": 1617667200, "is_pinned": false}, {"id": "UgwkOlyQDGkKnjm5J-V4AaABAg", "parent": "root", "text": "FRAUD. FRAUD. FRAUD... FRAUD\n\nFRAUD DONE BY ICICI LOMBARD GENERAL INSURANCE...\nPLEASE DONT BUY ICICI POLICY FOR YOUR CAR AND NOT EVEN FOR YOUR LIFE....\n\nThis is in regards to my Vehicle No:- DL9CAN-8800 i.e Honda City VX CVT bearing Policy No. 3001/HA-100306930/00/000 and Proposal No. P11525259 ON Dated:-31/03/2019. I always take insurance of my cars from ICICI LOMBARD and for the said vehicle I am getting insurance from Honda Assured by ICICI LOMBARD Since I have this Car. On Dated 31/03/2019, I got a call that your car policy is getting expire in next 3 months, So i am loyal customer of icici lombard I opted to renew my car insurance that time on 31/03/2019 and I got my new policy(2019-2020) before expiry of previous policy (2018-2019) with 25% NCB as i dint took any claim in that year till 31/03/19 which was expiring on 06/06/19. After Renewing new policy I met with an accident and I took two claims in my previous policy (2018-2019) in MAY and June Month 2019 and noone told me or remind me to pay 25%NCB which i got in new policy.\nEverything was running fine and we are not aware of giving back NCB to ICICI LOMBARD because it was renewed even before 3 months prior of expiry and Unfortunately I met with an accident on 15 December 2019 and on Delhi-Jaipur Highway, I dint get any help from ICICI LOMBARD Roadside Assistance which made me realize how worst this policy is....Not even this when i sent my vehicle to CHERISH HONDA, NEW DELHI , one of the inspection executive MR. RAHUL DAWAR told us that you will not get claim as u have hidden some facts from the ICICI LOMBARD INSURANCE CO. ...'' You hadn't told about the claim you had taken in previous policy and for that instance you got 25%NCB while renewing your new policy. So, After got to know this, immediately I Called up to customer care and initiate a NCB Recovery which I paid to ICICI LOMBARD GENERAL INSURANCE CO. instantely, But Today even after paying the NCB, Mr. RAHUL DAWAR emailed me itself to pay 25% of whole expenses by saying I am the Head which is totally out of my mind. Before Email, He was saying that I have emailed to ICICI LOMBARD about the decision whether to cover it in Zero Dep. or To take it as SUB-STANDARD and for this process he has wasted my 3 Days. I am also attaching an email for your reference.\n\nMy Questions are :-\n1. Who told you to do Insurance 3 months prior of expiry?\n2. Why ICICI LOMBARD had done my insurance 3 months prior of expiry?\n3. Why ICICI LOMBARD has not notify me to pay NCB when i had taken claims in previous year policy?\n4. Even after paying NCB, MR.RAHUL DAWAR is requesting me to pay 25% of expenses. So, Whats the point to pay back NCB?\n5. If ICICI does Insurance prior 3 months of expiry, then you should be aware of all this things and should notify customer about it.\n6. Why ICICI has not remind me to pay NCB?\n7. Is this my fault that i renewed my policy before 3 months of expiry?\n\nPlease try to answer my questions:\nI have 5 Cars with me and Always prefer to get insurance from ICICI LOMBARD but from today onwards, I will stick on my words ''NOT TO BUY SUCH A PATHETIC SERVICE OR POLICY'' Because this is totally fraud with customers even after being a LOYAL customer.\n\nI will go to Legal Authorities/ Consumer Court against this and would highlight this matter on social media too because this is a matter of Concern now.\nI am a Youtuber of Automobile Channel having more than (1.3 Million Subscribers) and will help my public by making such a nice video on this about what has happened with me by taking ICICI Policy, So that they never be think of buying ICICI Policy in their Life.\nI have Many Youtuber Friends of Automobile Channel who has followers more than me, Will take their help too to highlight this serious matter.\nWill make it Popular on FACEBOOK, INSTAGRAM too.\nKindly try to investigate in this matter because I Guess Your Surveyer is hiding some facts , he even does not know how to talk to customers. When I got his Contact no, He just said not to call me.\n\nRegards\nABHISHEK", "like_count": 1, "author_id": "UCDw-u5x_1568HQvwBdNFPMg", "author": "@abhisheksaini1909", "author_thumbnail": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_lqRThpTQ744eadC0yB9VAOnpLv0TH7uyP3g9r82AhuvZI=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "author_is_uploader": false, "author_is_verified": false, "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/@abhisheksaini1909", "is_favorited": false, "_time_text": "6 years ago", "timestamp": 1586131200, "is_pinned": false}, {"id": "UgzYQ1mR08hThC_GnYp4AaABAg", "parent": "root", "text": "icici lombard  insurance fraud company he bhai log inka insurance kbhi mt lena", "like_count": 5, "author_id": "UCpKWwNXQi9z50nzL6MJYlAg", "author": "@m100guru5", "author_thumbnail": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/9Hh5m5TpnxykSXDTd7AfVoFU9xJpzbCYcXAh25N1y_RLcmW36tpZ_MCcMESU8CP6TZK6HXVg2w=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "author_is_uploader": false, "author_is_verified": false, "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/@m100guru5", "is_favorited": false, "_time_text": "6 years ago", "timestamp": 1586131200, "is_pinned": false}, {"id": "Ugyvlk0HRRALOKirBuJ4AaABAg", "parent": "root", "text": "icici lombard  insurance fraud company he bhai log inka insurance kbhi mt lena", "like_count": 4, "author_id": "UCpKWwNXQi9z50nzL6MJY